Text: School TeachingVince I stopped by to see you today However Mrs Shirley notified me that you were out of the country Look I need another favor My wife whom you met last summer and I have been living in The Woodlands about a month now We have tried to no avail to get her in the local school district as a speech pathologist or a K grade school teacher She could easily find a teaching job in the Houston Independent School District However I would prefer that she taught locally in The Woodlands I need to know if you know of anyone we can contact to get her in The Woodlands School System I would greatly appreciate if you could help us out once again I am attaching her resume for your perusal Thanks A Million Vince Sincerely Datren Williams EES x
